headline.main: Town Grieving After Mother, 4 Children Die in House Fire
headline.print_headline: Town Grieving After Mother, 4 Children Die in House Fire

lead_paragraph: Thousands of protesters have marched through the Romanian capital of Bucharest to support the country's anti-corruption authority and demand that state institutions be free of political interference.
